2.AutoConfigurations: springboot
	provides auto-configurations to setup componenets automatically based upon dependeicies
springboot automatically confiure beans based on :
	classpath dependencies
	application.properties
	Annotations
for EG: if spring-boot-starter-data-jpa is present
then: Datasoure, entity manager, transaction manager are auto configured!!

