3.Embedded Server(Tomcat)
	applicaions are standalone with embedded server like tomact 
	no external server configurations setup is needed

4.Minimal Configurations | 5.Starter dependencies
	springboot support microserice architecture and is highly customzable
	comes with producion ready feature like healthhekcsmetricies and monitorings
	eliminate boiler plate code and xml configuration , letting devepers focus on business logics

5.optionated - means has some default like embedded tomcat default web container
6.Customizable - though it has some default , but easily customizable at any time during your 
		development time. if your prefer jetty you can change that, on pom file

